A Fremont man faces a felony charge of assaulting a healthcare provider as a result of his uncooperative and disruptive behavior on Friday .

Police were called to reports of a man passed out in the 200 block of North Main Street at about 9:30 p.m. Lt. Kurt Bottorff of the Fremont Police Department said Jonathan M. Warford , 29 , did not cooperate with police and continued his disruptive behavior after being transported to Fremont Area Medical Center .
